    "1 is 1.0"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "We can do boolean tests on lists as well:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 82,
   "metadata": {
